text: SURJ (Showing Up for Racial Justice) is an organization organizing white folks who may not know how to get involved or be effective allies. There's a national conference call this evening for anyone interested in knowing more or finding out how to help. <https://www.facebook.com/events/789145491221609/?active_tab=highlights>
